ActPort Authorities Management Regulations
Canada Marine Act
SubjectCertificate of Amalgamation for the Oshawa and Hamilton Port Authorities
PrecisOrder Certifying that the Hamilton Port Authority and the Oshawa Port Authority are amalgamated and continue as one port authority to be named the HAMILTON-OSHAWA PORT AUTHORITY, effective June 18, 2019.
